\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout

\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
After all points in the next frame are located, the output shape is back-transfo
rmed to the 
\begin_inset Formula $x\mbox{-}y$
\end_inset

 coordinate system.
 The last step is the employment of the statistical shape model.
 The shape is projected to the PCA subspace
\end_layout

